A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Part 3 of Article 8 of Chapter 14 of Title 44 of the Official Code of Georgia
2 Annotated, relating to mechanics and materialmen relative to liens, so as to provide for a fine
3 for any frivolous mechanic lien filed; to provide for related matters; to provide for an
4 effective date; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
5 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
6 SECTION 1.
7 Part 3 of Article 8 of Chapter 14 of Title 44 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated,
8 relating to mechanics and materialmen relative to liens, is amended by adding a new Code
9 section to read as follows:
10 "44-14-361.6.
11 Any lien filed pursuant to Code Section 44-14-361 that is made without substantial
12 justification or that is not made in good faith or that is made with malice or a wrongful
13 purpose, as such terms are defined in Code Section 51-7-80, shall be subject to a fine of
14 $1,500.00 per lien filed, in addition to any attorney's fees or court costs."
